room_title: Escape room "The Science Laboratory" by Escape St. Pete in Tampa
room_description:
You are assistants to the internationally renowned and respected geneticist Doctor A. B. Normal. During the performance of your normal daily duties, you discover that the evil doctor has been conducting illegal human cloning experiments, but before you can turn him over to the authorities he locks you in his lab in order to make his getaway.
You have one hour to decipher clues and solve puzzles in order to find out where he is going and to get proof of his criminal activities to the FBI before he can leave the country...
